# 🎵 Spotify Top 50 – Music Analytics Dashboard

## 📌 Project Overview
An interactive 3-page Power BI dashboard built on Spotify's 
Top 50 World dataset to help music analysts, playlist managers, 
and marketing teams monitor song and artist performance through 
consolidated visual insights.

## 📊 Dashboard Pages
- **Overview** – KPI cards, explicit vs non-explicit analysis,
  album type breakdown, monthly/yearly trend analysis
- **Artist** – Top artists by popularity, tracks per album,
  #1 chart position hits, artist-level drill-downs
- **Songs** – Song rankings, album/single distribution,
  detailed performance table by year

## 🛠️ Tools & Skills Used
- Power BI
- DAX (15+ custom measures)
- Data Visualization
- Data Analysis
- Business Intelligence

## 📐 Key DAX Measures Built
- Total Songs, Distinct Artists, Avg Popularity
- Explicit Song % , Non-Explicit Song %
- Avg Duration (converted from milliseconds)
- Position #1 Hits per Artist
- Year-level & Artist-level scoped measures

## 💡 Business Problem Solved
Spotify's raw Top 50 data was limited to basic lists and rankings.
This dashboard transforms it into an actionable decision-support 
tool — enabling teams to spot trends, compare content types, 
and identify artists worth promoting.

